{"tid":1977129,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蓬佩奧：中國應對疫情方式或令各國再考慮是否用華為","createTime":"2020-04-17T17:20:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T17:41:02.000Z","uid":81228,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"67c9654d3f688acf6b77ea26d3e410ae036ae8d3","tid":1977129,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T17:20:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1521272_1_20200417224651.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1521272_1_20200417224651.jpg&h=0f3c4c1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蓬佩奧說，中國在疫情下的角色，可能會迫使各國重新考慮他們的電訊基礎設施政策。（路透社資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n美國國務卿蓬佩奧表示，中國在新型冠狀病毒全球大流行中的角色，可能會迫使各國，重新考慮他們的電訊基礎設施政策，包括是否採用中國電訊設備商華為的5G網絡。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧接受霍士新聞訪問時，被問到有關華為與5G技術的問題時表示，他很有信心，中國共產黨現時未能透明、公開與適當地處理疫情相關資訊，將會令很多國家重新考慮他們在電訊建設方面的政策，當華為推銷他們的設備及硬件，這些國家將會換以另一個角度去作出決定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1521272-20200417.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1521272-20200417.htm&d=0xR7vGHOl893LUq1yoppeuUDsY8FkShsNjUL6uXjEIs%3D&h=c4d456b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1521272-20200417.htm&h=c89dbdf8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1521272-20200417.htm</a>"},{"pid":"da4f54bdb729df3ef3865ddcfb918ea99ca803e2","tid":1977129,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T17:22:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3e4cdb1908bd0bd6672153a6c021297a31119f9","tid":1977129,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T17:36:53.000Z","msg":"用華為咪武漢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b683c5c26ef6f1a1cd4ca51e5a0200fb0fcf756c","tid":1977129,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-0